Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take bayarwa don bunkasa Ilimin Artificial Intelligence
Yayin da China ke kara shiga harkar kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa kan bincike a fannin, in ji mai zuba jari da kuma mai amfani da kere kere Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Bayanan sun zo ne bayan da sassa daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka suka yi sanarwa game da ilimin artificial, kodayake Amurka ba ta da tsarin dabarun ilimin artificial a gaba ɗaya.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta sanar da shirin ta na shekarar da ta gabata, inda ta yi niyyar zama kasa mafi kyau a harkar kere-kere ta shekarar 2030.
"Samun kudaden bincike na AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, ganin cewa sauran ƙasashe sun fi Amurka ci gaba, kuma muna neman sabon abu a fannin AI", in ji Lee.
Dubban kudaden zai iya nufin ninka damar da za a samu na ganin an cimma babbar nasara a fannin ilimin kere kere a Amurka, Lee ya shaidawa CNBC a cikin wata hira da aka yi da shi a wannan makon.
Lee ya wallafa littafinsa mai suna "Al Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" tare da Houghton Mifflin Harcourt a wannan watan kuma shi ne Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kere kere na kasar Sin, Face++.
A Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a cikin 1980s, yana aiki a kan tsarin fahimtar mutum wanda ya sanya mafi kyawun wasan Othello a Amurka. Daga baya ya zama babban jami'in gudanarwa a Microsoft Research da shugaban kamfanin Google na China.
Lee ya gane gasar fasahar gwamnatin Amurka da ta gabata kamar Babban Shirin Binciken Harkokin Tsaro na Robotics Challenge, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da zai kasance na gaba don taimakawa wajen gano masu kallo na gaba.
Masu bincike a Amurka sukan yi aiki tukuru domin samun tallafin gwamnati, in ji Lee.
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke daukar shugabannin ilimi ba; kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi kokarin daukar dalibai masu hazaka daga jami'o'i don yin aiki a kan ilimin kere kere kwanan nan.
Har ila yau, Lee ya ce canje-canje a cikin manufofin ƙaura na iya taimaka wa Amurka ta ƙarfafa ƙoƙarinta a fagen ilimin kere kere.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da katunan kore ta atomatik ga mutanen da ke da ilimin kere kere", in ji shi.
Majalisar Jiha ta kasar Sin ta sanar da Shirin Ci gaban Kayan Aikin Artificial na Zamani na gaba a watan Yulin 2017.
Cibiyar Kimiyya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin tana ba da tallafi ga mutane a cibiyoyin ilimi kamar yadda National Science Foundation da sauran cibiyoyin gwamnati ke ba da tallafi ga masu bincike daga Amurka, amma ingancin aikin ilimi ya yi kasa a kasar Sin.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Hadin gwiwar Artificial Intelligence, wanda zai hada da abokan hulɗa daga masana'antu da kuma ilimi, kuma fadar White House ta sanar da cewa za a kafa Kwamitin Gwargwadon Artificial Intelligence.
A wannan watan DARPA ta sanar da saka hannun jari a wani shiri mai suna AI Next.
