Paris fashion nuna cewa latest tarin m tufafi ne game da isa your babban titi
Idan kana son wani hat ko kuma kana son ka hana rana fita, wannan shi ne salon da ya dace da kai.
Masu zanen kaya Valentino da Thom Browne sun bayyana manyan kayan kwalliya masu ban sha'awa don tarin su na SS19 a kan fashi, wanda ya haskaka a kan saitin salo a makon Paris Fashion Week.
An yi wasu kyawawan huluna a kan Instagram a wannan bazarar kuma an ga manyan abubuwan da waɗannan masu zanen kaya suka yi a fagen salon.
