LeBron zai buga wasan farko da Lakers a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Za a gama jiran masoya da ke fatan ganin LeBron James ya fara wasa a Los Angeles Lakers.
Luke Walton, kocin Lakers, ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa ta farko a ranar Lahadi a San Diego.
Amma bai yanke shawarar na tsawon minti zai yi wasa a sake.
"Za a yi fiye da ɗaya amma ƙasa da 48," in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai buga wasan ne a cikin 'yan mintoci kaɗan.
Bayan wani zaman atisaye a farkon makon, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na shirin wasan Lakers na wasanni shida kafin fara kakar wasa.
"A wannan lokaci na aikina ba na bukatar wasannin kafin kakar wasa don yin shiri", in ji shi.
Lokacin Taron Yammacin Virginia Trump, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Trump ya fara jerin tarurrukan yakin neman zabe a wannan daren a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurruka biyar da aka shirya domin mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da ziyarar wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka dage zaben tabbatar da zabinsa a kotun koli, Trump na neman samun goyon baya a zaben tsakiyar shekara, domin 'yan jam'iyyar Republican na fuskantar hatsarin rasa iko a majalisa idan aka kada kuri'ar a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne taron Trump a West Virginia yau da dare kuma ta yaya zan iya kallon sa a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia a karfe 7 na yammacin ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon gangamin Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar amfani da YouTube live stream.
Trump na iya tattauna sauraron da za a yi a wannan makon game da nadin da ya yi wa babban alkalin kotun Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ke fuskantar matsin lamba sakamakon zargin cin zarafin mata da ya yi da kuri'ar da aka amince da shi a majalisa, an dage shi har tsawon mako guda, har sai FBI ta gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban manufar jerin tarukan shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaɓe mai wuya a watan Nuwamba su sami ɗan ci gaba.
Kamfen din Shugaba Trump ya ce za a yi gangamin gangamin jam'iyyun biyar a mako mai zuwa da nufin "karfafawa masu aikin sa kai da masu goyon baya a yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma karawa da rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da na wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Samun iko da majalisa na da muhimmanci a ajandarmu har sai da shugaban ya yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama yayin da ya fara babban lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda bai bayyana sunansa ba, ga Reuters.
Ana gudanar da shi a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na yau da dare na iya kawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma samun kulawa daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
Ranar Asabar za ta zama ziyarar Trump ta biyu a watan jiya a West Virginia, jihar da ta samu maki sama da 40 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar dan majalisar wakilai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a cikin kuri'un kuri'un.
"Ba abu mai kyau ba ne ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo nan don ya ba shi damar shiga cikin kuri'un kuri'un", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Gasar Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA na nuna kwallaye don ci gaba da gwagwarmaya yayin da za su shiga wasannin mutum-mutumin ranar Lahadi
Bayan an kammala zaman na uku da takwas, wasan hudu na ranar Asabar na iya zama daidai abin da ake bukata don wannan gasar Ryder Cup.
Aikin da ake yi na samun karfin gwiwa, ra'ayi ne da aka yi tunaninsa a duniyar wasanni, amma kuma ra'ayi ne da 'yan wasa ke gaskatawa da shi, musamman a irin wannan gasa.
To, ina za su ce akwai ƙarfin hali a yanzu?
"Sun kasance maki shida a gaba kuma yanzu sun kai hudu, don haka muna da ɗan ƙarfi a gare ni", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake barin ranar.
Hakika, Turai tana da fa'ida, maki huɗu a kan tudu da kuma sauran goma sha biyu da za a buga.
Kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, 'yan Amurkan na jin cewa suna da ɗan iska a cikin yanayin su kuma suna da isasshen ƙarfafawa, musamman daga Speith da Justin Thomas waɗanda suka yi wasa tare a duk rana kuma suka sami maki uku daga hudu.
Speith ya yi fice a kan kujerar kuma yana kafa misali mai kyau.
The scrapers na bikin tafi sama kamar yadda suka zagaye tafi gaba, gudanar da wani muhimmin fare don samun a game hudu da daya ko da yake shi da Thomas ya kasance a ƙasa biyu bayan biyu.
Akwai irin wannan rikici bayan da suka ci wasan a ranar 15, irin wannan rikici wanda ke gaya muku cewa ba ku yi imani Amurka ta sake fita ba.
"Dole ne ku mai da hankali kuma ku damu da kanku", in ji Speith.
Wannan shi ne kawai abin da wadannan 'yan wasan da a yanzu.
18 ramuka don yin wani ra'ayi.
'Yan wasa guda daya da suka ci maki fiye da Speith da Thomas a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, labarin da ba za a iya mantawa da shi ba na gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Ma'aurata suna da 'yanci amma suna son Turai hudu a hudu kuma suna yin komai a can.
Moliwood shi ne kawai mashaya da ba a yi bargo a ranar Asabar da yamma, kuma ba a yi bargo a ranar Asabar da safe, ranar Alhamis da yamma ko kuma a karfe tara na karshe na ranar Alhamis.
Wannan tafiyar, da kuma yadda suke jujjuyawar makamashi tsakanin su da kuma taron, sun tabbatar da cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su fafata ranar Lahadi, wanda zai fi shahara wajen tabbatar da nasarar Turai a gasar cin kofin duniya fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari.
Idan zai yiwu biyu a wannan farashin a kan daban-daban yadudduka.
Amma, ya yi saurin magana game da cin nasarar Turai.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun sa Sergio Garcia, gwarzon kwallon hudu na safe, cikin sauki lokacin da aka yi masa takara da Alex Noren.
Bayan buga wasa biyu da ninki biyu a farkon tara, Mutanen Espanya da Sweden sun shiga cikin rami wanda ba su kusa fita ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, ba wanda zai taimake ka ka fita daga cikin ramin.
Wuraren hudu da kuma wasan kwallon kafa suna da ban sha'awa don kallo saboda dangantakar da ke tsakanin 'yan wasa, shawarar da suke bayarwa, shawarar da ba su bayar ba da kuma yadda dabarun zasu iya canzawa a cikin wani lokaci.
Ya zuwa yanzu Turai ta fi kyau a matsayin ta kuma sun yi gaba sosai a farkon ranar karshe, amma wasan na kwana hudu ya tabbatar da cewa Team USA na da ikon yin kokawa, wani abu da wasu musamman a Amurka suka yi shakku a kai.
Turai ne a kan gaba da 10-6 a ranar karshe na Ryder Cup
Turai na da gagarumar dama a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan kammala wasannin kwallon kafa hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar da ci 10-6 a gaban Amurka.
Abokan gaba Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci yakin neman zabe tare da nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods don ɗaukar ƙimar su har yanzu a Le Golf National zuwa maki huɗu.
Dan wasan Turai Thomas Bjorn, wanda ke neman dawo da kyautar bayan da ya yi a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya mamaye dan wasan Amurka a wasanni hudu da safe, inda ya ci gaba da ci 3-1.
Amurka ta kara adawa a zagayen hudu, amma ba za ta iya kawar da matsalar ba.
'Yan wasan Jim Furyk suna bukatar maki takwas daga wasanni 12 na ranar Lahadi domin su ci gaba da samun nasara.
Fleetwood ita ce ta farko da ta samu maki hudu a jere a gasar, kuma shi da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da "Molliwood" bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, su ne na biyu da suka samu maki hudu a wasanni hudu na gasar Ryder Cup.
Bayan Woods da Patrick Reed sun yi nasara a wasanni hudu, sai suka yi aiki tare don doke Woods a kan Bryson Starters na Amurka da 5 da 4.
Wood, wanda ya yi wasa biyu a ranar Asabar, ya samu wasu dama na musamman amma ya yi rashin nasara 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 a wasanni hudu da hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da wasan kwallon kafa na safe, ya koma matsayin dan wasan Henrik Stenson a wasan kusa da na hudu, inda ya doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka a karo na farko da na uku a duniya da 2 da 1.
Ba abin da ya faru a Turai a ranar farin ciki da kuma sanyi a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Jordan Spieth, wanda ya lashe manyan wasanni uku, da Justin Thomas sun kafa misali ga 'yan Amurka da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun ci Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain da 2 da 1 a cikin kwallaye huɗu kuma daga baya suka ci Polter da Rory McIlroy da 4 da 3 a cikin kwallaye huɗu bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup ne kawai ƙungiyar ta dawo daga maki huɗu a baya a farkon wasannin mutum, kodayake ana buƙatar daidaitaccen ƙimar kawai a kan ƙungiyar Furyk tunda su ne masu riƙe da ƙwallon ƙafa.
Amma, bayan kasancewa a biyu ga kwana biyu, samun a cikin hasken ranar Lahadi kama da idan ya kasance bayan your ikon.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta amince da amincewa da juna ba
A ranar Asabar, ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa takunkumin na ci gaba da karfafa mummunan tunani a Amurka kuma kasar ba za ta kawar da makaman nukiliya ba a kan irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron kungiyar ta shekara-shekara cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki matakan kyautata niyya a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da atisayen nukiliya da jiragen sama, lalata tashar gwajin nukiliya, da kuma alkawarin kada a yada makaman nukiliya ko fasahar nukiliya.
Amma ba mu ga irin wannan martani daga Amurka ba, "in ji shi.
Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba za a sami amincewa a cikin tsaron kasa ba kuma a irin wannan yanayi ba za mu iya fara amincewa da kanmu ba.
Duk da cewa Ri ya maimaita korafin da Koriya ta Arewa ta yi na kin amincewa da matakin da Amurka ta dauka na rage makaman nukiliya inda za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada idan ta dauki matakai na rage makaman, wannan sanarwa ta kasance mai ban mamaki saboda ba ta ki amincewa da matakin da aka yanke na rage makaman nukiliya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da sanarwar hadin gwiwa tsakanin Kim John Un da Donald Trum a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka na yanzu da kuma shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, inda Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan "rashin lalata makaman nukiliya na yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi kokarin ganin an kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara ba da makaman nukiliya.
Har ila yau, Washington ta yi watsi da kira ga sassauta takunkumin kasa da kasa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka na neman a fara kare makaman nukiliya da farko kuma suna kara matsa lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinsu ta hanyar tilastawa, kuma har ma suna adawa da sanarwar kawo karshen yakin", in ji RI.
"Ikon da takunkumi ke da shi na cin mu mafarki ne na mutanen da ba su san kome ba game da mu.
Amma matsalar ita ce, takunkumi na ci gaba da karfafa mugun zato.
Ri bai yi magana ba game da shirin sake ganawa tsakanin Kim da Trump, taron da shugaban ya yi tawaye a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya mako guda da ya gabata.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya ambaci tarurruka uku da Kim ya yi da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin kwanaki biyar da suka gabata, ya kara da cewa: "Idan Koriya ta Kudu ce jam'iyyar da ke da alhakin batun kare makaman nukiliya ba Amurka ba, to kare makaman nukiliya na Koriya ta Kudu ba zai kai ga irin wannan rashin yiwuwar ba".
Amma jawabin Ri ya bambanta da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harin da Amurka ta kai wa Koriya ta Arewa ba zai yiwu ba bayan da "Mista Trump" ya kira Kim "rakitin" a kan aikin kai-da-kai.
A Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar lalata Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya, ya yaba wa Kim saboda karfin gwiwar da ya nuna wajen daukar matakan gyara, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a dage takunkumin har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta daina amfani da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da takamaiman lokacin da za a yi wannan, yana mai cewa "idan ya dauki shekaru biyu, uku ko watanni biyar - babu matsala".
China da Rasha sun yi jayayya cewa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kamata ta ba Pyongyang lada saboda matakan da aka dauka.
Amma, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya fada wa Babban Taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Ya kamata a aiwatar da takunkumin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da karfi kuma ba tare da izini ba har sai mun tabbatar da tabbatar da cikakken kare makaman nukiliya.
Kwamitin Tsaro ya amince ya kara takunkumin da ya kafa kan Koriya ta Arewa a 2006 domin ya yi kokarin takaita kudaden da ake baiwa Pyongyang don shirin nukiliya da kuma harkokin sufuri.
Ri ya gana da Pompeo a gefen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe domin shirya taron na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma ba a kai ga ziyarar da ta gabata ba.#
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa an samu ci gaba, amma Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge shi cikin sa'o'i na yin "gwagwarmaya kamar 'yan bindiga".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin ganawa da Moon a wannan watan domin ta gyara tashar watsa shirye-shiryen da kuma tashar nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki matakan da suka dace.
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa abubuwan da yake nema sune tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya bayar a Singapore da kuma matakan daidaita dangantakar da Amurka.
Dalibai na Harvard suna samun dama ga shakatawa
Wani sabon darasi a Harvard yana sa dalibai su samu karin barci a wannan shekara domin su yi kokarin magance al'adun macho na yin karatu dare da rana tare da amfani da maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗalibai a manyan jami'o'i a duniya sau da yawa suna da rashin fahimta game da abubuwan da suka fi muhimmanci.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a kan maganin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women ya tsara wannan darasi, wanda ya yi imanin shine na farko na irin wannan a Amurka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare shi ne a farkon karatun bayan ya ba da jawabi kan tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
A ƙarshen jawabin wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, "Me ya sa na san wannan ne yanzu da nake shekara ta ƙarshe?"
Ya ce babu wanda ya gaya masa muhimmancin barci - abin mamaki ne a gare ni", in ji shi a Telegraph.
Wannan darasi, wanda aka fara gabatar da shi a wannan shekara, yana bayyana wa ɗalibai yadda halayen bacci masu kyau ke taimakawa aikin ilimi da na wasanni, tare da inganta lafiyarsu gaba ɗaya.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma shugaban ayyukan kula da lafiyar jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan gano cewa dalibai suna fama da mummunar rashin bacci a cikin mako.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya ya ƙunshi jerin ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A cikin wani sashe akwai hoton ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai ke danna kan kofi, takalma da littattafai don koyo game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da yadda rashin bacci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki, da mahimmancin halayen bacci mai kyau.
A wani sashe kuma, mahalarta sun koyi yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci ke ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, ciwon ciki da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, taswirar harabar makarantar, tare da gumaka masu ma'ana, ta ƙarfafa mahalarta su yi tunani game da ayyukan yau da kullum.
Mun san cewa ba za mu canja halayen ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun ga cewa suna da hakkin su san - kamar yadda kuke da hakkin ku san yadda shan sigari ke shafar lafiyarku", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Al'adar alfahari da zama a barcin dare har yanzu tana nan, in ji shi, ya kara da cewa, fasahar zamani da karuwar matsin lamba kan dalibai na nufin rashin bacci ya zama matsala da ke kara muni.
Tabbatar da cewa kana samun isasshen bacci, kuma na inganci, ya kamata ya zama hanya ga dalibai su magance damuwa, sanyin gwiwa da damuwa, in ji shi - har ma don kauce wa matsa lamba, saboda rashin bacci yana sa kwakwalwa ta yi tunanin kana bacci, yana sanya ka cikin damuwa a kowane lokaci.
Raymond So, wani dalibi dan shekara 19 daga California da ke nazarin ilimin sunadarai da kuma ilimin halittu, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara wannan darasi, bayan ya yi karatu a daya daga cikin darussan a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya buɗe masa idanu kuma ya sa ya yi ƙoƙarin samun wannan darasi ga dukan harabar.
Yana fatan cewa mataki na gaba zai bukaci dukkan ɗaliban karatun digiri su kammala irin wannan tsarin karatun kafin su shiga ƙungiyar gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da kafa ƙararrawa don barci, da kuma farkawa, kuma su san da illa mai illa na hasken wuta da aka saki ta fuskokin lantarki da hasken LED, wanda zai iya shafar motsin zuciyarku kuma ya haifar da matsalolin bacci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: raga da Menga doke Gerrard maza
Rangers sun sake fuskantar mummunan wasa a gida yayin da Dolly Menga ta ci kwallo ta haifar da asara 1-0 ga Steven Gerrard a Livingstone.
Ibrox na neman nasarar farko a hanya tun bayan da suka doke St Johnstone 4-1 a watan Fabrairu, amma Gary Holt Gerrard ya buga kwallo karo na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin kungiyar wanda ya bar kungiyar ta maki takwas a baya da shugabannin kungiyar Ladbrokes wato Hearts.
Menga ya ci kwallo da minti bakwai kafin rabin lokaci kuma Rangers sun kasance masu gajeren lokaci kuma ba su da damar yin wasa.
Yayin da Rangers yanzu suka sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingstone ya hau zuwa na uku kawai a bayan Hibernian akan bambancin haske.
Kuma akwai yiwuwar samun karin matsala ga Rangers bayan da mai wasan Calum Spence ya yi fama da ciwon kai bayan da wani abu ya fadi a kan masu ziyara.
Gerrard ya yi sau takwas a cikin tawagar da ta kai Ayr zuwa wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfred.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt ya tsaya tare da 11 da suka doke Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda tawagarsa ta yi nasara a kan abokan hamayyarsu a kowane lokaci.
Rangers sun fi rinjaye a kan mallaka amma Livingstone ya fi yin hakan da ƙwallo lokacin da suke da ita.
Ya kamata su ci kwallo bayan minti biyu bayan da Menga ya ba Scott Pittman damar zura Allan McGregor amma dan wasan ya yi watsi da damar da ya yi ta buga kwallo a fili.
Keaghan Jacobs ya yi amfani da tsalle mai zurfi don gano kyaftin Craig Halkett amma abokin aikinsa Alan Lithgow ba zai iya samun damar ba.
Rangers sun mallaki amma akwai fatan da yawa fiye da imani a cikin wasan karshe na wasan.
Alfredo Morelos ya ji cewa ya kamata a kashe shi a cikin mota bayan kusan awa 15 bayan shi da Steven Lawless suka yi masa duka amma alkali Steven Thomson ya yi watsi da roƙon Colombiad.
Rangers sun yi harbi biyu a raga a farkon rabin wasan amma sai dan wasan Ibrox Liam Kelly ya samu sauki da ciwon Lassana Coulibaly da kuma harbin Ovie Ejaria.
Duk da cewa Livi ya ci kwallo bayan minti 34 ya yi nasara a wasan, babu wanda zai ce sun cancanci hakan saboda kokarin da suka yi.
Duk da haka, Rangers sun yi amfani da hanyoyin magance Jacobs da kuma shirin da ya dace.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya wuce ƙwallon ƙafa zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya yi mamaki lokacin da ya wuce zuwa Menga don sauƙi.
Gerrard ya kasance a matsayin mai birki yayin da ya canza Coulibaly don Ryan Kent kuma ya kusan canzawa kai tsaye lokacin da mai tsaron gidan ya wuce Morelos amma Kelly ya yi birki a layin don toshe shi.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da tilasta wa masu kallo su yi irin wasan da suke so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna karbar dogon kwallon bayan dogon kwallon.
Holt's squad zai iya ƙarawa zuwa ga ƙimar a cikin minti na ƙarshe amma McGregor ya tashi da kyau don dakatar da Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya rasa penny daga kusurwa.
Mai tsaron gidan Rangers Glenn Middleton ya sake neman a kashe shi bayan ya yi karo da Jacobs amma Thomson ya sake soke wannan bukatar.
