HIV/Aids: China ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na sabbin kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan al'ummarta da ke rayuwa da cutar HIV da kuma cutar AIDS.
Jami'an kiwon lafiya sun ce fiye da mutane 820,000 ne ke fama da cutar a kasar.
An gano sabbin cututtuka kusan 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin lamura sun kasance ta hanyar jima'i, suna nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri ta wasu sassan Tsiyen ta hanyar isar da jini bayan kamuwa da cutar.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV a wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, a shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya karu da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a shekarar 1997, amma ana cewa nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT yana da ban tsoro.
Saboda dabi'u na gargajiya na kasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70% zuwa 90% na mazajen da suke jima'i da mazaje za su auri mata a ƙarshe.
Yawancin yaduwar cututtuka sakamakon rashin tsaro ne na jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangin.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani bangare na shirin magance matsalar.
