Amurka na iya amfani da jirgin ruwa don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren cikin gida
Washington na iya amfani da jirgin ruwa idan ya cancanta don hana makamashin Rasha zuwa kasuwa, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke ya bayyana, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya ce shiga tsakani na Rasha a Syria - musamman, inda take aiki bisa gayyatar da gwamnatin halal ta yi - ya zama hujja don bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
