A wannan lokacin jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da Shugaba Donald Trump da kansa, sun yi kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga shirin samar da bututun mai mai suna Nord Stream 2, wanda Trump ya ce Berlin ta zama alhakin Moscow.
