Jakadan Amurka ya zargi Tsiena da cin zarafin mutane da yada labarai
A mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani shafi hudu na talla a jaridar Amurka da ke tallata amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafofin yada labarai na Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
A ranar Laraba ne shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da karamin jaridar China Daily a Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi kowa samun karbuwa a jihar Iowa - bayan da ya zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Jami'an Amurka sun shaida wa Reuters cewa zargin da Trump ya yi cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka wani mataki ne na gaba a wani yunkuri na kara matsa lamba kan China.
Ko da yake al'ada ce gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace da ke inganta kasuwanci, a halin yanzu Beijing da Washington suna fama da yakin kasuwanci wanda ya sa kasashen biyu suka sanya takunkumi kan kayayyakin da ke shigowa daga juna.
An fara amfani da takunkumin da China ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya don kai wa masu fitar da kayayyaki hari a jihohi kamar Iowa da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na Amurka da China.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wani yanki a cikin Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, "Sai dai yanzu China ta tabbatar da wannan cin zarafin ta hanyar gudanar da tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin jaridarmu mai 'yanci".
"Ta hanyar yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin China tana amfani da muhimman al'adun Amurka na 'yancin ra'ayi da' yancin latsawa ta hanyar sanya sanarwar da suka biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin haka, a cikin kantin sayar da jaridu a kan titi a nan Beijing, za ka ga cewa yana da wuya a samu muryoyin da ba su jitu ba kuma ba za ka ga ainihin tunani na ra'ayoyi daban-daban da mutanen China ke da shi game da hanyar tattalin arziki da ke damun kasar Sin ba, saboda jaridar tana karkashin jagorancin jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", ya rubuta.
Ya kara da cewa, "wani daga cikin manyan jaridun kasar Sin ya ki amincewa da buga labarin nasa, ko da yake bai ce wane ne ba".
Masu Nazarin Sun Yi Gargadin Cewa 'Yan Jam'iyyar Republican Za Su Yi Wa Mata Tsananin Zabe Kafin Zaben Zamani Tare Da Kavanaugh
Yayin da wasu 'yan jam'iyyar Republican suka goyi bayan nadin Brett Kavanaugh a kotun koli a kan zargin da ake yi na lalata da shi, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za su ga yadda za a mayar da martani, musamman daga mata, a lokacin zaben da ke tafe.
Tunanin wannan lamari ya yi yawa, kuma jam'iyyar Republican ta riga ta ce za ta ci gaba da kada kuri'ar.
Ba za ku iya cire waɗannan abubuwan ba, "in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse a wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Lahadi.
Reeher ya ce yana da shakku ko kokarin da Sanata Jeff Flake (Arizona) ya yi na minti na karshe na samun bincike daga FBI zai isa ya shawo kan masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta da gobe ko Nuwamba ba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu fafutuka ta MoveOn a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington, D.C.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zanga sun yi ihu suna cewa "Mutumin Nuwamba ya zo!" yayin da suka yi zanga-zanga a harabar majalisar dokoki yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dokta Christine Blasey Ford, in ji Mic.
"Himma da himmar 'yan Democrat za su yi yawa", in ji Stu Rothenburg, wani mai nazarin siyasa, ga shafin labarai.
Mutane suna cewa suna da himma; gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya ƙaruwa, musamman a tsakanin mata marasa tsaro a gefen gari da kuma tsakanin matasa masu jefa ƙuri'a, 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ko da yake ba sa son shugaban ƙasa sau da yawa ba sa jefa ƙuri'a.
Ko da kafin Ford ya ba da shaida a fili game da zargin da ya yi wa shugaban kasa na neman takarar kotun koli, bincike ya nuna cewa za a yi gagarumin martani idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da takarar.
"Wannan ya zama babban abin da ya shafi 'yan Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Wannan ba wai kawai game da kuri'ar kwamitin ba ne ko kuma kuri'ar karshe ko za a jefa Kavanaugh a benci, amma kuma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka yi da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", in ji Guy Cecil, daraktan Priorities ISA, wata kungiya da ke taimakawa zaben 'yan Democrat, a kan tashar labarai.
Amma dai, da alama Amurkawa sun yi ta murabus a kan wanda za su yi wa takara bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, tare da samun karin damuwa game da Kavanaugh.
Wani sabon binciken ra'ayi da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41% na masu amsa sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35% suka ce sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce sun yi imanin tabbas ko wataƙila Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari kawai suka ce haka game da Ford.
Bayan harin da Flake ya kai, FBI yanzu tana binciken zargin da Ford ya yi tare da akalla wani mai gabatar da kara, Deborah Ramirez, in ji jaridar Guardian.
Ford ta yi shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata hari a lokacin da ta ke 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ya yi ikirarin cewa Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada shi a kotun koli, ya sace mata al'aura yayin da suke wata liyafa a lokacin da suke karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda Ya kirkiro Yanar Gizo na Duniya Yana Shirin Fara Sabon Yanar Gizo Domin Mu Haɗa Hannu Da Google Da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kafa sabuwar kamfani da zai yi kokari wajen gasa da Facebook, Amazon da kuma Google.
Sabon aikin kamfanin Inrupt, wani kamfani ne wanda ke gina kan Berners-Lee Solid open source platform.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar a wane lokaci ne ake adana bayanan su kuma wa zai iya samun damar wane bayani.
A cikin wata hira da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi watsi da cewa manufar kamfanin Inrupt ita ce "sarrafa duniya".
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", in ji kamfanin.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi ko POD.
Zai iya ƙunsar jerin lambobi, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalanda, laburaren kiɗa da sauran albarkatu na sirri da na sana'a.
Yana da kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna samuwa a kan mai bincike ɗaya kuma suna tare a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke na musamman game da ajiyar bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa yana da cikakken ikon mai amfani wanda ke ganin wane irin bayani.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "aikin sirri ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce na Kamfanin, ita ce kamfanin ya kawo albarkatu, matakai da kuma ƙwarewar da ta dace don taimakawa wajen tabbatar da cewa kowa yana da Solid.
A halin yanzu kamfanin ya hada da Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro daga IBM, masu haɓaka da aka yi wa kwangila don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma al'ummar masu sa kai.
A farkon wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba su ta amfani da albarkatun da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi kadai ne ke magana da Facebook da Google game da gabatar da canji gaba daya inda ake jujjuya tsarin kasuwancin su gaba daya cikin dare.
Ba ma neman izininsu.
A cikin wani sakon da ya wallafa a Medium ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa, Inrupt na son samar da makamashi da kuma tsarin kasuwanci don taimakawa wajen kare inganci da ingancin sabon shafin da ake kirkira a Solid.
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi ga Intanet lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara kan bambancin intanet.
Bayan fara Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa Founder da Daraktan Cibiyar Talla ta Duniya, da Talla ta Duniya, da kuma Cibiyar Bayanai ta Open.
"Ina matukar fatan wannan mako mai zuwa zai zama na tarihi a tarihin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
