An Sake Yi Wa Jamus Tsaro A Wani Sabon Jirgin Yakin
Ya kamata a fara aiki da sabon firiji na jirgin ruwan Jamus a 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba zai kasance ba har sai a kalla shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin daidaito da kuma tsada, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
An dage fara aiki da "Rheinland-Pfalz", babban jirgin sabon Baden-Wuerttemberg-class refrigerators, har zuwa farkon rabin 2019, kamar yadda jaridar Die Zeit ta ruwaito ta hanyar magana da yawun rundunar sojin.
Ya kamata jirgin ya shiga cikin Jirgin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin bayan bayarwa sun lalata ci gaban wannan aikin mai matukar muhimmanci.
Jirgin ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da kamfanin ya yi wa kwastomomi a 2007 za su maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwan na Bremen.
An ce za su hada da makamai masu ƙarfi, sararin samaniyar iska da na jiragen ruwa tare da wasu fasahohin asiri, kamar sa hannun radar, infrasound da sauti mai saurin ragewa.
Sauran muhimman halaye sun haɗa da tsawon lokutan kiyayewa - sabon firiji ya kamata ya iya tabbatarwa har zuwa shekaru biyu daga tashoshin gida.
Amma jinkiri na ci gaba yana nufin cewa jiragen yakin basasa - wanda zai ba wa Jamus damar jefa ikonta a teku - za su shuɗe a lokacin da za su fara aiki, Die Zeit ta ce.
Firijin F125 ya kasance cikin kanun labarai a bara, bayan da Jaridar Jamus ta ki amincewa da jirgin ya koma tashar jiragen ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da kamfanin ya mayar da jirgin zuwa ga masu ginin jirgin bayan an kawo shi.
Dalilin dawowar jirgin bai bayyana ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun yi nuni da wasu mahimman kayan aiki da kayan aiki wadanda ke nufin cewa jirgin ruwan ya zama mara kyau idan ya yi yaƙi.
Rashin ingantattun kayan aikin ya kasance mai mahimmanci saboda jiragen Baden-Wuerttemberg zasuyi aiki da rundunar masu jiragen ruwa 120 - kawai rabin lambobin da ke kan masu jigilar Bremen.
Har ila yau, an gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai wanda zai iya lalata aikinsa kuma ya rage ikon Navy don ƙara ƙarin haɓaka a nan gaba.
An yi imanin cewa "Rheinland-Pfalz" mai nauyin 7,000 ya ninka irin jiragen da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga rashin kayan aiki, farashin duk aikin - gami da horar da ma'aikatan - ya fara zama matsala.
An ce ya kai €3.1billion ($3.6bn) - sama da €2.2billion da farko.
Matsalar sabbin firiji na zama mafi mahimmanci yayin da ake jin gargaɗin kwanan nan cewa ƙarfin bankin Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaron majalisar dokokin Jamus ya amince cewa jirgin ruwan ya "fito daga jiragen ruwa da za a iya gano su".
