Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Central Sulawesi, a ƙarshen bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da haihuwa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka afkawa.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai faɗi wanda ya kai tsawon fiye da kilomita 300 (180 miles) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin 2017, lardin, yanki na yanki, yana da yawan jama'a 299,200.
Kamun kifi da noma sune manyan masu kula da tattalin arzikin lardin Central Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
